title: on me by section 1(2) of the Road Traffic and Roads Act 2023 (No. 16 of 2023),
heading: 1. This Order may be cited as the Road Traffic and Roads Act 2023
text_raw:
1. This Order may be cited as the Road Traffic and Roads Act 2023 

(Commencement) Order 2023.
text_norm: 1 order may cited road traffic road act 2023 (commencement) order 2023

title: on me by section 1(2) of the Road Traffic and Roads Act 2023 (No. 16 of 2023),
heading: 2. The 17th day of July 2023 is appointed as the day on which the following
text_raw:
2. The 17th day of July 2023 is appointed as the day on which the following 
provisions of the Road Traffic and Roads Act 2023 (No. 16 of 2023) shall come 
into operation: 

(a) Part 1; 

(b) 

section 42(d); 

(c) 

sections 43, 45, and 47. 

GIVEN under my Official Seal, 

14 July, 2023. 

EAMON RYAN, 

Minister for Transport. 

Notice of the making of this Statutory Instrument was published in 
"Iris Oifigiúil" of 21st July, 2023.
